{"tid":1631992,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"大家千萬唔好同啲藍絲講政府其實呃緊佢地","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:49.000Z","uid":14678,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"acbee0af40d030fbc17db75ac076f6dfbf57a6c6","tid":1631992,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:45:34.000Z","msg":"我地照舊星期2去撳哂啲錢先，等啲藍絲有錢都要充公<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n人所共知 支那打貿易戰打到無哂錢，除咗香港救到佢地之外根本就無人救到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以呢個所謂嘅蒙面法由同到尾都只係為控制資產救支那\b而鋪路<br />\n今晚出多個聲明就更加無私顯見私，此地無銀300兩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢只係唔想我地撳走哂香港啲錢而救唔到大陸<br />\n我有朋友係銀行高層（一人之下個隻），佢話真係唔講得出嚟，但係為咗大家著想我都決定要爆個消息出嚟<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">星期2 ATM同銀行櫃枱都唔會有好大量現金提供，政府要控制香港嘅現金流！！！好多有錢人已經偷偷地轉哂資產做美金，香港經濟爆破係遲早嘅事，政府而家係滅緊聲同控制緊港人資產，所以，拎錢走啊！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n<br />\n記得同自己人講，撳走哂啲錢佢<br />\n等班傻仔藍絲仲信政府啊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"293c026794453d5421c939170d05875f6b2e6dac","tid":1631992,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:47:41.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"e37d1f1efc290a931dfaa28b933d2f697ad8a780","tid":1631992,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:48:47.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"3c9be70dc90946ba32fdca8bfa5f45e8ceb8a91a","tid":1631992,"uid":248019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:11.000Z","msg":"今日行左6 7個地方都禁唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比佢地知<br />\n比我禁左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37a1f3b88a92adc5cdce86c6cf1471a381eedbc4","tid":1631992,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c9be70dc90946ba32fdca8bfa5f45e8ceb8a91a","tid":1631992,"uid":248019,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:49:11.000Z","msg":"今日行左6 7個地方都禁唔到錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好比佢地知<br />\n比我禁左先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:50:21.000Z","msg":"係，同自己人講好啦<br />\n唔好傳出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a923d6263021d0439a1f144e1f147755fb8582","tid":1631992,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:17.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"ee8b72982bd5bb216612348f8da385542d075da4","tid":1631992,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:51:53.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"08b055188a0805e51cfbcbab16775be39265d951","tid":1631992,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:52:37.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"76c9dc6c94b0f96a370358c2bbb7b7ad9e1f7fab","tid":1631992,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:53:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"64470b9e547080af031130973e87ea1dbe3d8a30","tid":1631992,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:54:28.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"9a0a4e3c954e38fd36e27490ddf773b43621f6a0","tid":1631992,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:25.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"d5d4d878aee98e9e4a73a277a6f260a17d4cac3b","tid":1631992,"uid":14678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc